name: Misty Japanese Countryside
description: Sun breaks over a quiet little village in rural japan.  I've always admired the slow and deliberate lifestyle of people in the Japanese countryside.  I have absolutely no idea what life is really like there, but I would like to imagine it includes lots of walks in nature.  I'm drawn by the depictions by Ghibli studio and Miyazaki of chirping cicadas and wind rolling through the grass and trees.  Something about it...
